    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Catalina's Horror Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After Catalina's mother takes her to an abandoned arcade, our protagonist finds herself trapped in a strange and terrifying dimension that seems to have been inhabited by humans decades ago.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We are left alone, and our goal is to escape and find our mother.</strong><br><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040670/extras/24f589570fc8e1be2ef068ea808cb743.avif?t=1764544842\" width=1408 height=398 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During our terrifying adventure, we will encounter many varied and dark places, monstrous inhabitants, two main species, children who were lost long ago, and enemies that are practically divine.<br><br>We will realize that humans had already inhabited that dimension, but why were they there? More importantly, why are they no longer there? Embark on this terrifying adventure and discover all the secrets behind this dimension known as “The World.”  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040670/extras/e3ad5481d727c9136b64ee840537d258.avif?t=1764544842\" width=1440 height=534 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Catalina's Horror Adventure mixes various genres such as psychological horror, puzzles, adventure, and shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a game designed to rediscover every corner, as it is full of little secrets and Easter eggs that expand the lore of the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040670/extras/655c6de021324d0baafb3b533771825c.avif?t=1764544842\" width=1440 height=559 /></span></p>",
